title: STAR WARS Jedi: Survivor Jedi Training Sessions Trailer with Mark Hamill
description:
Watch as Mark Hamill pops in to offer actor Cameron Monaghan some advice on his role as Jedi Cal Kestis in STAR WARS Jedi: Survivor. Mark offers his sage wisdom as well as some questionable training methods as he hopes to give Cameron the edge he needs as he continues his journey from STAR WARS Jedi: Fallen Order.

title: ARMORED CORE VI FIRES OF RUBICON Official Gameplay Trailer
description:
